data.description: "ACADIAN DELIGHT" Sitting pretty on oversized lot with lush landscaping, plenty of parking & detached 2 car garage. Your sure to appreciate the huge open kitchen with center island, plenty of cabinets & counter space. Great room has custom built-in cabinets & shelving for all your nick knacks.  Primary bedroom & bath located upstairs; bath has gorgeous vanity & 6' soaking tub. Privacy fenced backyard with covered patio & outside storage shed. Extras...Newer roof, 2 tankless water heaters, whole house generator, 2017...windows, new floors, updated kitchen, 3 bathrooms remodeled, floors & light fixtures.
